reviewText: DO NOT waste your money! It has hardly any correct information, it loops the same clips repeatedly, and it plays the same stupid elevator music the entire time. I watched it with a friend and she was disappointed that I had to keep correcting what was supposed to be informative. The people who are commentating are people who seem to have no real knowledge of pop culture or her career and make points that make no sense at all. This is a horrible, disgusting piece of trash. If you're a true Britney fan AVOID THIS GARBAGE AT ALL COSTS!
